    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TolE0148">
<l>vēṟṟumaik kaṇṇum valleḻut talvaḻi</l>
<l>mēṟkū ṟiyaṟkai yāvayi ṉāṉa</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those two non-vocalized consonants [i.e. <foreign xml:lang="ta">ṅ</foreign> and <foreign xml:lang="ta">ṉ</foreign>]</l>
<l>standing [as final members] do not manifest</l>
<l>any change in non-case relation,<note
              place="foot"><foreign xml:lang="ta">vēṟṟumai yalvaḻi.</foreign> E.g. <foreign xml:lang="ta">maṇ|poṉ niṟutti, maṇ|poṉ kaṭitu, maṇ|poṉ ciṟitu</foreign> etc.</note> whatever sound</l>
<l>appears initially.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
